\capbrief supports the bindless API and resource access in shaders. Todo
May need to split into multiple caps as some drivers do not support buffers. Bug
\nswitch is experimental support and so is not a constant cap yet. \platformtable{hasBindless,c,a,c,a,c,c,r,r,r,r,r}

\capbrief hasRayTraceOpacityMicroMapTriangleArrays provided by \nvidia extension.
This is a mutual exclusive feature cap with hasRayTraceOpacityMicroMapTriangleArrays. Where hasRayTraceOpacityMicroMapTriangleArrays indicates support all OMM features by the core API / multi vendor extensions. hasNvidiaRayTraceOpacityMicroMapTriangleArrays indicates implementation of OMM by the \nvidia driver with driver extensions.
\someNYI \platformtable{hasNvidiaRayTraceOpacityMicroMapTriangleArrays,c,a,c,a,c,c,c,r,c,c,c}
